      "location": "Anti-Patterns section",
      "description": "Add anti-pattern for 'using arbitrary Tailwind values (w-[347px]) instead of theme tokens' since this breaks design system consistency which the skill emphasizes."
    },
    {
      "type": "improvement",
      "location": "Implementation Plan (Step 5)",
